<section class="home-hero">
    <p class="home-tag">Smart Budgeting for Students</p>
    <h1>Student Budget Tracking System</h1>
    <p class="home-intro">
        The Student Budget Tracking System is a web-based application designed to help students
        manage their allowance, monitor expenses, and keep track of their remaining balance in a
        simple and organized way.
    </p>
</section>

<section class="home-overview">
    <div class="home-card">
        <h2>Project Overview</h2>
        <p>
            This system allows users to record daily budget entries, categorize expenses, review
            transaction history, and generate visual summaries through dashboard reports and charts.
            It provides students with an accessible tool for understanding their spending habits
            and making better financial decisions.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="home-card">
        <h2>Main Purpose</h2>
        <p>
            The main goal of this project is to promote financial awareness, discipline, and
            responsible budgeting among students. By using this system, students can develop
            better money management habits and gain a clearer view of how they spend their allowance.
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="home-card">
        <h2>Key Features</h2>
        <ul class="home-features">
            <li>Add and manage budget records</li>
            <li>Track allowance and expenses</li>
            <li>View remaining balance instantly</li>
            <li>See recent transactions on the dashboard</li>
            <li>Generate summary reports with charts</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</section>
